folders:
node_modules - where all the dependencies are installed
public - manifest.json:for progressive web apps, index.html:the only HTML file in app
src - where the main JS file and all other components will be present/coded

files:
.gitignore - the files mentioned here will be ignored during git commands like commit,stage etc
package-lock.json - entire dependency tree & their versions
package.json - only main dependencies and their versions
README.md
